spec_data.Name: nodejs-single-line-log
spec_data.Description:
Node.js module that keeps writing to the same line in the console (or
a stream). Very useful when you write progress bars, or a status message
during longer operations. Supports multilines.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 04:06:48 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Keep writing to the same line in the terminal
